The '''1987 [[Syracuse Orange football|Syracuse Orangemen football]] team''' represented [[Syracuse University]] in the [[1987 NCAA Division I-A football season]]. The team finished 11&ndash;0&ndash;1 and tied [[1987 Auburn Tigers football team|Auburn]] in the [[1988 Sugar Bowl]].
